<head>
 
  <title>Active & Passive Voice</title>
</head>

<body>
  <h1 style="color: blue">Active to passive </h1>
  <strong style="color: red">continuous tense </strong>
 <p style="color: fuchsia">
  <i>Active : I am drawing a picture.</i>
  <br>
  <b>passive : A picture is being drawn by me.</b>
  <hr>
  </p>
  <p style="color: green">
    <i>Active : The teacher was correcting answer papers. </i>
  <br>
  <b>Passive : Answer papers were being corrected by the teacher.</b>
  <hr>
  </p>
  <p style="color: orange">
    <i>Active : We are buying vegetables.</i>
    <br>
    <b>Passive : vegetables are being bought by us </b>
  </p>
 
 </p>
</body>

</html>